Additionally, the paper mentions image-captioning tasks, which are often associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of reward learning also suggests a connection to reinforcement learning (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses classification algorithms, which could also place it in the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
